<lb n="0898c03" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><note n="0898008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本，【甲】策子第二十帖，【乙】黃蘗版淨嚴等校訂加筆本塚本賢曉氏藏，【丙】大日本縮刷大藏經，（（都部…卷））八字＝（（陀羅尼門諸部要目））八字【三】【甲】，（（陀羅尼門諸部要目一卷））十字【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0898008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">【原】麗本，【甲】策子第二十帖，【乙】黃蘗版淨嚴等校訂加筆本塚本賢曉氏藏，【丙】大日本縮刷大藏經，（（都部…卷））八字＝（（陀羅尼門諸部要目））八字【宋】【元】【明】【甲】，（（陀羅尼門諸部要目一卷））十字【乙】【丙】</note><app word-count="8" n="0898008"><lem wit="【大】">都部陀羅尼目一卷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">陀羅尼門諸部要目</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">陀羅尼門諸部要目一卷</rdg></app><note n="0898008" type="rest" place="foot">【原】麗本，【甲】策子第二十帖，【乙】黃蘗版淨嚴等校訂加筆本塚本賢曉氏藏，【丙】大日本縮刷大藏經</note></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0898c04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0898c05" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0898009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔開府…智〕三十三字－【宋】【元】，開府儀同王司＝唐【明】【乙】【丙】，〔開府…譯〕四十六字－【甲】</note><note n="0898009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔開府儀同王司特進試鴻臚卿肅國公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒正號大廣智大興善寺三藏沙門不空奉詔譯〕四十六字－【甲】，〔開府儀同王司特進試鴻臚卿肅國公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒正號大廣智〕三十三字－【宋】【元】，開府儀同王司＝唐【明】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0898009"><lem wit="【大】">開府儀同王司特進試鴻臚卿<note n="0898010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔肅國…寺〕二十五字－【明】【乙】【丙】</note><app word-count="25" n="0898010"><lem wit="【大】">肅國
<lb n="0898c06" ed="T"/>公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒
<lb n="0898c07" ed="T"/>正號大廣智大興善寺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>三藏沙門
<lb n="0898c08" ed="T"/><note n="0898011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（大廣智）＋不【三】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0898011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（大廣智）＋不【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0898011"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】">大廣智不</rdg></app>空奉　詔譯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">大興善寺三藏沙門不空奉詔譯</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【乙】【丙】">唐特進試鴻臚卿肅國公食邑三千戶賜紫贈司空諡大鑒正號大廣智大興善寺三藏沙門不空奉詔譯</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0898c09" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0898c0901">瑜伽本經都十萬偈。有十八會。初會經名一
<lb n="0898c10" ed="T"/>切如來真實攝。其經說五部。佛部<note place="inline">毘盧遮那佛以為部主</note>
<lb n="0898c11" ed="T"/>金剛部<note place="inline">阿&CB00434;佛<note n="0898012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（以）＋為【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】＊</note><note n="0898012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（以）＋為【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】＊</note><app n="0898012"><lem wit="【大】">為</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">以為</rdg></app>部主</note>寶部<note place="inline">寶生佛以為部主</note>蓮花部<note place="inline">阿彌陀佛以為部主</note>羯
<lb n="0898c12" ed="T"/>磨部<note place="inline">不空成就佛以為部主</note>彼五部主。<note n="0898013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">各＋（各）【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0898013"><lem wit="【大】">各</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">各各</rdg></app>有四菩薩以為
<lb n="0898c13" ed="T"/>眷屬。前右左背而安列。四內供養。各屬四
<lb n="0898c14" ed="T"/>部。次第應知。四外供養亦屬四部。四門鉤索
<lb n="0898c15" ed="T"/>鎖鈴。四部次第應知。</p>
<lb n="0898c16" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0898c1601">又有四方賢劫中十六大菩薩。表賢劫中一
<lb n="0898c17" ed="T"/><note n="0898014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">切＝千【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0898014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">切＝千【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0898014"><lem wit="【大】">切</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">千</rdg></app>菩薩。</p>
<lb n="0898c18" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0898c1801">又外有五類天。一一類有四天。總有二十<note n="0898015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔天〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0898015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔天〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0898015"><lem wit="【大】">天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0898c19" ed="T"/>并<note n="0898016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔妃〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0898016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔妃〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0898016"><lem wit="【大】">妃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>后。</p>
<lb n="0898c20" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0898c2001">復有五類成二十。五類者上界四天。</p>
<lb n="0898c21" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT18p0898c2101"><l><note n="0898017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">乙本朱註曰此四句非頌而今分句而書之誤矣</note>住虛空四天</l><l>遊虛空四天</l>
<lb n="0898c22" ed="T"/><l>地居<note n="0898018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔有〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0898018"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0898019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">四天＝天四【甲】＊</note><app n="0898019"><lem wit="【大】">四天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">天四</rdg></app></l><l>居地底<app source="0898019" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">四天</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">天四</rdg></app></l></lg>
<lb n="0898c23" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0898c2301">瑜伽部曼<note n="0898020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">茶＝荼【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】下同</note><note n="0898020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">茶＝荼【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】下同</note><app n="0898020"><lem wit="【大】">茶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">荼</rdg></app>羅有四。一金剛界。二降三世。
<lb n="0898c24" ed="T"/>三遍調伏。四一切義成就。此四曼茶羅。表毘
<lb n="0898c25" ed="T"/>盧遮那佛內四智菩<note n="0898021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">薩＝提【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0898021"><lem wit="【大】">薩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">提</rdg></app>。<note n="0898022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔謂金…矣〕三十二字－【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0898022" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="a"/>〔謂金…矣〕三十二字－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note>謂金剛灌頂蓮花
<lb n="0898c26" ed="T"/>羯磨為四智。</p>
<lb n="0898c27" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0898c2701">又四智謂大圓鏡平等性妙觀察成所作為四
<lb n="0898c28" ed="T"/>智矣。又一一曼茶羅。建立六曼茶羅。所謂大
<lb n="0898c29" ed="T"/>曼茶羅。三昧耶曼茶羅。法曼茶羅。羯<note n="0898023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">磨＝摩【甲】</note><app n="0898023"><lem wit="【大】">磨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">摩</rdg></app>曼
<pb n="0899a" id="T18.0903.0899a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0899a01" ed="T"/>茶羅。四印曼茶羅。一印曼茶羅。唯降三世曼
<lb n="0899a02" ed="T"/>茶羅具十曼茶羅。餘皆具六<note n="0899001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔曼茶羅〕－【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0899001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔曼茶羅〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899001"><lem wit="【大】">曼茶羅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>一切印
<lb n="0899a03" ed="T"/>契一切法要。以四智印攝盡。大智印。以五相
<lb n="0899a04" ed="T"/>成本尊瑜伽。三昧耶<note n="0899002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（智）＋印【乙】</note><app n="0899002"><lem wit="【大】">印</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">智印</rdg></app><note place="inline">以二手和合金剛縛發生成印</note>。</p>
<lb n="0899a05" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0899a0501">法智印<note place="inline">名本尊種子法身三摩地一切契經文義</note>羯磨智印<note place="inline">以二<note n="0899003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔手〕－【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0899003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔手〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899003"><lem wit="【大】">手</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>金剛拳如執持器
<lb n="0899a06" ed="T"/>仗<note n="0899004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00124;幟＝標熾【甲】＊</note><app n="0899004"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00124;幟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">標熾</rdg></app>如身威儀形</note>。</p>
<lb n="0899a07" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0899a0701">又瑜伽中四種<note n="0899005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">眼＋（法眼）【三】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0899005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">眼＋（法眼）【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899005"><lem wit="【大】">眼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】">眼法眼</rdg></app><note place="inline">敬愛<note n="0899006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔法〕－【三】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0899006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔法〕－【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899006"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>。熾盛眼<note place="inline">鉤召</note>忿怒眼<note place="inline">降伏
<lb n="0899a08" ed="T"/>心殺害煩惱<note n="0899007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔也〕－【三】【甲】＊，【乙】</note><note n="0899007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔也〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】＊，【乙】</note><app n="0899007"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>慈<note n="0899008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔悲〕－【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0899008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔悲〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899008"><lem wit="【大】">悲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>眼<note place="inline">除毒<anchor id="fxT18p0899a01"/>息<note n="0899009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">怨＝冤【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0899009"><lem wit="【大】">怨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">冤</rdg></app><note n="0899010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔敵〕－【三】</note><note n="0899010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔敵〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0899010"><lem wit="【大】">敵</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>也</note>。</p>
<lb n="0899a09" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0899a0901">又一切如來教集瑜伽中。一百二十種護摩。
<lb n="0899a10" ed="T"/>依二十五種<note n="0899011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">爐＝壚【甲】</note><app n="0899011"><lem wit="【大】">爐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">壚</rdg></app>。<note n="0899012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔於〕－【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0899012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔於〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899012"><lem wit="【大】">於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>護摩爐中。<note n="0899013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">契＝執【三】【甲】</note><note n="0899013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">契＝執【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0899013"><lem wit="【大】">契</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">執</rdg></app>印<app source="0899004" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00124;幟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">標熾</rdg></app>
<lb n="0899a11" ed="T"/>各異。所求迅速成<note n="0899014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">辦＝辨【宋】</note><app n="0899014"><lem wit="【大】">辦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">辨</rdg></app>。世間出世間成就果
<lb n="0899a12" ed="T"/>報。諸會浩汗文義稍多。恐<note n="0899015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">文繁＝繁文【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0899015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">文繁＝繁文【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899015"><lem wit="【大】">文繁</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">繁文</rdg></app>。且略指方
<lb n="0899a13" ed="T"/>隅。依毘盧遮那成道經。大本十萬偈。可有三
<lb n="0899a14" ed="T"/>百卷經。唐國所譯略本七卷。此經中。說一百
<lb n="0899a15" ed="T"/>六十心十緣生句。<note n="0899016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔及〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0899016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔及〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0899016"><lem wit="【大】">及</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>五輪。地輪水輪火輪風
<lb n="0899a16" ed="T"/>輪空輪<app source="0899007" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>。此經中。二種修行。菩提心以為
<lb n="0899a17" ed="T"/>因。大悲以為根<note n="0899017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔本〕－【三】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0899017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔本〕－【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899017"><lem wit="【大】">本</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>方<note n="0899018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">便＋（以）【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899018"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">便以</rdg></app>為究竟。依勝義世
<lb n="0899a18" ed="T"/>俗。<note n="0899019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二諦〕－【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0899019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔二諦〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899019"><lem wit="【大】">二諦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>若依勝義修行。建立法身曼茶羅。
<lb n="0899a19" ed="T"/>是故此經中說。先<note n="0899020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">稱＝絣【三】【乙】【丙】，抨【甲】</note><note n="0899020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">稱＝絣【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】，＝抨【甲】</note><app n="0899020"><lem wit="【大】">稱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】">絣</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">抨</rdg></app>虛空中曼茶羅。是故
<lb n="0899a20" ed="T"/>觀本尊法身。遠離形色猶如虛空。住如是三
<lb n="0899a21" ed="T"/>摩地。若依世俗諦修行。依四輪以<note n="0899021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">為＝作【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899021"><lem wit="【大】">為</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">作</rdg></app>曼茶
<lb n="0899a22" ed="T"/>羅。本尊。</p>
<lb n="0899a23" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0899a2301">聖者若黃色。住地輪曼茶羅<note place="inline">其形方名金輪</note>聖者若白
<lb n="0899a24" ed="T"/>色。住水輪曼茶羅<note place="inline">其形圓名水輪</note>聖者若赤色。住火輪
<lb n="0899a25" ed="T"/>曼茶羅<note place="inline">其形三角</note>聖者若<note n="0899022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">青＋（色）【元】【明】</note><app n="0899022"><lem wit="【大】">青</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">青色</rdg></app>若<note n="0899023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">黑＋（色）【元】【明】</note><app n="0899023"><lem wit="【大】">黑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">黑色</rdg></app>。住風輪曼茶羅
<lb n="0899a26" ed="T"/><note place="inline">其形如半月</note>大曼茶羅安於八葉蓮花臺。五佛四菩
<lb n="0899a27" ed="T"/>薩安於臺葉。中曼茶羅外。又有三種曼茶羅。
<lb n="0899a28" ed="T"/><note n="0899024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一者〕－【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0899024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一者〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899024"><lem wit="【大】">一者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>一切如來曼茶羅。<note n="0899025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二者〕－【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0899025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔二者〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899025"><lem wit="【大】">二者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>釋迦牟尼曼
<pb n="0899b" id="T18.0903.0899b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0899b01" ed="T"/>茶羅。<note n="0899026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔三者〕－【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0899026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔三者〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899026"><lem wit="【大】">三者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>文殊師利曼茶羅。此曼茶羅。名
<lb n="0899b02" ed="T"/>為大悲胎藏曼茶羅。<note n="0899027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔若〕－【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】＊</note><note n="0899027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔若〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】＊</note><app n="0899027"><lem wit="【大】">若</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>弟子受灌頂法。小曼
<lb n="0899b03" ed="T"/>茶羅極微妙委曲。餘部所不代。此中修行供
<lb n="0899b04" ed="T"/>養。兼存二種<note n="0899028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔法謂〕－【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0899028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔法謂〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899028"><lem wit="【大】">法謂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>事與理<note n="0899029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔為二也〕－【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0899029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔為二也〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899029"><lem wit="【大】">為二也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>此經中。
<lb n="0899b05" ed="T"/>護摩火天有四十種。就中一十二種火為最勝。
<lb n="0899b06" ed="T"/>爐形及木。有乳果類苦練。所用各不同。東西
<lb n="0899b07" ed="T"/>南北祈願各殊。內外護摩亦依五輪。求四種
<lb n="0899b08" ed="T"/>事速疾成就。息災增益降伏敬愛。所請火天
<lb n="0899b09" ed="T"/>各<note n="0899030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔各〕－【甲】</note><app n="0899030"><lem wit="【大】">各</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>不同。寂靜熙怡忿怒喜怒。次第應知。</p>
<lb n="0899b10" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0899b1001"><app source="0899027" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">若</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>蘇悉地經。教中依三部。所謂佛部<note place="inline">五佛頂等</note>蓮
<lb n="0899b11" ed="T"/>花部種類甚多。金剛部金剛薩埵等。變化無
<lb n="0899b12" ed="T"/>量。有三種三昧耶。佛部蓮花部金剛部。有三
<lb n="0899b13" ed="T"/>部心真言。</p>
<lb n="0899b14" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0899b1401" type="dharani">爾那<note n="0899031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">爾＝羅【三】</note><note n="0899031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">爾＝羅【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0899031"><lem wit="【大】">爾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">羅</rdg></app>迦<note place="inline">半音呼<note n="0899032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔一〕－【三】</note><note n="0899032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔一〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0899032"><lem wit="【大】">一</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>阿嚧<note n="0899033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">力＋（迦）【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899033"><lem wit="【大】">力</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">力迦</rdg></app><note place="inline">二</note>&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>地<note n="0899034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">叨＝力【三】，力迦【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0899034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">叨＝力【宋】【元】【明】，＝力迦【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899034"><lem wit="【大】">叨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">力</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">力迦</rdg></app>
<lb n="0899b15" ed="T"/><note place="inline"><note n="0899035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔二合〕－【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0899035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔二合〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899035"><lem wit="【大】">二合</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app></note><note place="inline">三</note></p>
<lb n="0899b16" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0899b1601">部主有三種。金輪王佛頂佛部主。蓮花部主
<lb n="0899b17" ed="T"/>馬頭觀自在。金剛部主三世勝金剛。</p>
<lb n="0899b18" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0899b1801">三種部母。<note n="0899036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">佛部乃至母三十二字甲本作細註</note><note n="0899036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（佛部佛眼以為部母蓮花部白衣觀自在以為部母金剛部忙麼&CB00470;菩薩以為部母）三十二字本文＝（佛部佛眼以為部母蓮花部白衣觀自在以為部母金剛部忙麼&CB00470;菩薩以為部母）三十二字細註【甲】</note><app n="0899036"><lem wit="【大】">佛部佛眼以為部母。蓮花部白衣
<lb n="0899b19" ed="T"/>觀自在以為部母。金剛部忙麼&CB00470;菩薩以為
<lb n="0899b20" ed="T"/>部母</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><note place="inline">佛部佛眼以為部母蓮花部白衣觀自在以為部母金剛部忙麼&CB00470;菩薩以為部母</note></rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0899b21" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0899b2101">三種明妃。<note n="0899037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">佛部乃至妃三十六字甲本作細註</note><note n="0899037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（佛部無能勝菩薩以為明妃蓮花部多羅菩薩以為明妃金剛部金剛孫那利菩薩以為明妃）三十六字本文＝（佛部無能勝菩薩以為明妃蓮花部多羅菩薩以為明妃金剛部金剛孫那利菩薩以為明妃）三十六字細註【甲】</note><app n="0899037"><lem wit="【大】">佛部無能勝菩薩以為明妃。蓮花
<lb n="0899b22" ed="T"/>部多羅菩薩以為明妃。金剛部金剛孫那利
<lb n="0899b23" ed="T"/>菩薩以為明妃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><note place="inline">佛部無能勝菩薩以為明妃蓮花部多羅菩薩以為明妃金剛部金剛孫那利菩薩以為明妃</note></rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0899b24" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0899b2401">三種忿怒。<note n="0899038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">不動乃至怒二十三字甲本作細註</note><note n="0899038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（不動尊佛部忿怒忿怒鉤蓮花部忿怒軍茶利金剛部忿怒）二十三字本文＝（不動尊佛部忿怒忿怒鉤蓮花部忿怒軍茶利金剛部忿怒）二十三字細註【甲】</note><app n="0899038"><lem wit="【大】">不動尊佛部忿怒。忿怒鉤蓮花部
<lb n="0899b25" ed="T"/>忿怒。軍茶利金剛部忿怒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><note place="inline">不動尊佛部忿怒忿怒鉤蓮花部忿怒軍茶利金剛部忿怒</note></rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0899b26" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0899b2601">有四種界。<note n="0899039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">金剛乃至界二十五字甲本作細註</note><note n="0899039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（金剛橛地界金剛牆八方界金剛網上方界密縫阿三莽儗&CB00135;界）二十五字本文＝（金剛橛地界金剛牆八方界金剛網上方界密縫阿三莽儗&CB00135;界）二十五字細註【甲】</note><app n="0899039"><lem wit="【大】">金剛橛地界。金剛牆八方界。金
<lb n="0899b27" ed="T"/>剛網上方界。密縫。阿三莽儗&CB00135;界</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><note place="inline">金剛橛地界金剛牆八方界金剛網上方界密縫阿三莽儗&CB00135;界</note></rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0899b28" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0899b2801">又有四種界。結護曼茶羅。<note n="0899040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">金剛乃至方二十六字甲本作細註</note><note n="0899040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（金剛索護東方金剛幢幡護西方金剛迦利護南方金剛&CB00123;護北方）二十六字本文＝（金剛索護東方金剛幢幡護西方金剛迦利護南方金剛&CB00123;護北方）二十六字細註【甲】</note><app n="0899040"><lem wit="【大】">金剛索護東方。
<lb n="0899b29" ed="T"/><note n="0899041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔金剛〕－【甲】</note><app n="0899041"><lem wit="【大】">金剛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>幢幡護西方。金剛迦利護南方。金剛&CB00123;
<pb n="0899c" id="T18.0903.0899c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0899c01" ed="T"/>護北方</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><note place="inline">金剛索護東方金剛幢幡護西方金剛迦利護南方金剛&CB00123;護北方</note></rdg></app>。又大界名商羯羅。設佛頂<note n="0899042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔護〕－&M062485;【乙】</note><sic n="0899042" resp="【乙】" corr="＆lac；">護</sic>輪王
<lb n="0899c02" ed="T"/>等&CB00444;近。不被障礙。此經中。修真言者成就世
<lb n="0899c03" ed="T"/>間悉地。依時<note n="0899043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔依〕－【甲】</note><app n="0899043"><lem wit="【大】">依</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>處。時者謂三時。處謂本尊
<lb n="0899c04" ed="T"/>像前。<note n="0899044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔有〕－【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0899044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔有〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899044"><lem wit="【大】">有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>供養五種。除閼伽。一者塗香。二<note n="0899045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔者〕－【甲】＊</note><app n="0899045"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0899c05" ed="T"/>花鬘。三<app source="0899045" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>燒香。四<app source="0899045" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>飲食。五<app source="0899045" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>燈明。白
<lb n="0899c06" ed="T"/><note place="inline">北</note>黃<note place="inline">東</note>黑<note place="inline">南</note>赤<note place="inline">西</note>隨息災增益降伏敬愛。所求
<lb n="0899c07" ed="T"/>應知。成就者十八種物隨身。<note n="0899046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">廣如＝如廣【甲】</note><app n="0899046"><lem wit="【大】">廣如</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">如廣</rdg></app>經說。</p>
<lb n="0899c08" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0899c0801">三時澡<note n="0899047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">浴＝洗【三】【甲】</note><note n="0899047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">浴＝洗【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0899047"><lem wit="【大】">浴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">洗</rdg></app>三時<note n="0899048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">換＝浣【三】【甲】</note><note n="0899048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">換＝浣【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0899048"><lem wit="【大】">換</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">浣</rdg></app>衣。一月分為四時。<note n="0899049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔從〕－【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0899049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔從〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899049"><lem wit="【大】">從</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>月
<lb n="0899c09" ed="T"/>生一日至八日。應作息災。從九日至十五日。
<lb n="0899c10" ed="T"/>應作增益。從十六日至二十三日。應作降伏。
<lb n="0899c11" ed="T"/>從二十四日至月盡日。為敬愛法。<note n="0899050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB03476;＝&CB13836;【宋】【元】【甲】，&CB08019;【明】，蕤【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0899050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB03476;＝&CB13836;【宋】【元】【甲】，＝&CB08019;【明】，＝蕤【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899050"><lem wit="【大】">&CB03476;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【甲】">&CB13836;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&CB08019;</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">蕤</rdg></app>呬<note n="0899051" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">耶＝邪【三】【乙】</note><note n="0899051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耶＝邪【宋】【元】【明】【乙】</note><app n="0899051"><lem wit="【大】">耶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】">邪</rdg></app>
<lb n="0899c12" ed="T"/>經亦同蘇悉地。<note n="0899052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔說〕－【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】＊</note><note n="0899052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔說〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】＊</note><app n="0899052"><lem wit="【大】">說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>分布曼茶羅。及絣地法。
<lb n="0899c13" ed="T"/>此經中極微細。不可具錄。</p>
<lb n="0899c14" ed="T"/><p id="pT18p0899c1401"><note n="0899053" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">又＝及【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0899053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">又＝及【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899053"><lem wit="【大】">又</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">及</rdg></app>八方。其護持帝王營從兵法。五天竺國深
<lb n="0899c15" ed="T"/>敬信佛法。於帝王可傳。蘇婆呼童子經。此經
<lb n="0899c16" ed="T"/>中<app source="0899052" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0899054" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">辦＝辯【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0899054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">辦＝辯【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899054"><lem wit="【大】">辦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">辯</rdg></app>求成就人護摩。杵金銀銅鐵石水精
<lb n="0899c17" ed="T"/><note n="0899055" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">佉＝法【宋】</note><app n="0899055"><lem wit="【大】">佉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">法</rdg></app>陀羅木等。無量種各不同杵。五<note n="0899056" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">股＝般【甲】＊</note><app n="0899056"><lem wit="【大】">股</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">般</rdg></app>三<app source="0899056" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">股</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">般</rdg></app>
<lb n="0899c18" ed="T"/>一<app source="0899056" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">股</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">般</rdg></app>。長十六指為上。十二指為中。八指<app source="0898012" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">為</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">以為</rdg></app>
<lb n="0899c19" ed="T"/>下。乃至一指節<note n="0899057" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔者〕－【三】【甲】，【乙】【丙】＊</note><note n="0899057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔者〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】，【乙】【丙】＊</note><app n="0899057"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>為下。此經中說。不持金
<lb n="0899c20" ed="T"/>剛杵。<note n="0899058" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔念誦者〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0899058" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔念誦者〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0899058"><lem wit="【大】">念誦<app source="0899057" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>無由得成就。金剛<note n="0899059" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">鈴＝杵【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0899059" resp="CBETA" type="mod">鈴＝杵【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0899059"><lem wit="【大】">鈴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">杵</rdg></app>者。<note n="0899060" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔是般…是〕十二字－【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0899060" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔是般…是〕十二字－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app word-count="12" n="0899060"><lem wit="【大】">是
<pb n="0900a" id="T18.0903.0900a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0900a01" ed="T"/>般若波羅蜜義金剛杵者是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">&lac;</rdg></app>。菩提心義。能壞
<lb n="0900a02" ed="T"/>斷<note n="0900001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔常〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0900001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔常〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0900001"><lem wit="【大】">常</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>二邊。契<note n="0900002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">合中道＝中道中【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0900002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">合中道＝中道中【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0900002"><lem wit="【大】">合中道</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">中道中</rdg></app>。有十六菩薩位。亦表
<lb n="0900a03" ed="T"/>十六空為中道。兩邊各有五<app source="0899056" type="＊"><lem wit="【大】">股</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">般</rdg></app>。五佛五智
<lb n="0900a04" ed="T"/>義。亦表十波羅蜜。能摧十種煩惱。成十種真
<lb n="0900a05" ed="T"/>如。便證十地。證金剛三<note n="0900003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">摩地＝業【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0900003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">摩地＝業【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0900003"><lem wit="【大】">摩地</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">業</rdg></app>獲金剛智。坐
<lb n="0900a06" ed="T"/>金剛座。亦是一切智智。亦名如來自覺聖智。
<lb n="0900a07" ed="T"/>若不修此三摩地智。得成佛者。無有是處。恐
<lb n="0900a08" ed="T"/>文繁不能廣述。若廣釋。窮劫不可說盡。<note n="0900004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">怚＝怛【三】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0900004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">怚＝怛【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0900004"><lem wit="【大】">怚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】【丙】">怛</rdg></app>
<lb n="0900a09" ed="T"/>唎三昧耶經。同毘盧遮那集會。所有聖眾修
<lb n="0900a10" ed="T"/>行教法。自性成就。此教中修行者。但住菩提
<lb n="0900a11" ed="T"/>心。大悲志願。不捨無盡眾生界。所<note n="0900005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（（不應…犯））十三字＝（（應不違事設違之不應食啗若有食者不成破））十八字【三】，（（應不違事設違之不應食噉若食者不成破））十七字【甲】，（（應不違爭設違之不應食噉若有食者不成破））十八字【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0900005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（（不應…犯））十三字＝（（應不違事設違之不應食啗若有食者不成破））十八字【宋】【元】【明】，＝（（應不違事設違之不應食噉若食者不成破））十七字【甲】，＝（（應不違爭設違之不應食噉若有食者不成破））十八字【乙】【丙】</note><app word-count="13" n="0900005"><lem wit="【大】">不應事
<lb n="0900a12" ed="T"/>不可建不可食若為者犯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">應不違事設違之不應食啗若有食者不成破</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">應不違事設違之不應食噉若食者不成破</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">應不違爭設違之不應食噉若有食者不成破</rdg></app>三<note n="0900006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">摩耶＝昧耶戒【三】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><note n="0900006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">摩耶＝昧耶戒【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="0900006"><lem wit="【大】">摩耶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】【丙】">昧耶戒</rdg></app>。此經中。說
<lb n="0900a13" ed="T"/>誦大輪金剛真言。不染諸愆過。以為方便。現
<lb n="0900a14" ed="T"/>生一切真言速疾成就。此經中不動尊等。四
<lb n="0900a15" ed="T"/>十<note n="0900007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二＋（地）【乙】</note><app n="0900007"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">二地</rdg></app>如來<note n="0900008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">僮僕＝僕童【甲】</note><app n="0900008"><lem wit="【大】">僮僕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">僕童</rdg></app>使者。若修真言行菩薩。堅
<lb n="0900a16" ed="T"/>持菩提心。我等承事供養擁護。食彼修行者
<lb n="0900a17" ed="T"/>殘食。彼等至無上菩提諸<note n="0900009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔有作〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0900009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔有作〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0900009"><lem wit="【大】">有作</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>障者毘那夜
<lb n="0900a18" ed="T"/>迦不。得<note n="0900010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔其〕－【三】【甲】</note><note n="0900010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔其〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0900010"><lem wit="【大】">其</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】">&lac;</rdg></app>便。速證無上菩提。</p>
